    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just protecting my sanity though. it's like, what's the point of even being here to witness the end? if everything is just going to be destroyed anyway, isn't it better to just leave on my own terms instead of waiting for the world to take everything from me? it feels like the only way to actually have control over something.",
